name: MixTape Headz NFT: Ukraine Edition Charity Auction

metadata.name: MixTape Headz Ukraine Edition #1
metadata.description: The MixTape Headz Society: Ukraine Edition is an ultra-rare collection of MixTape Headz NFTs specifically created to raise funds for charities supporting the crisis in Ukraine. Minted using the ERC-721 token standard on the Ethereum blockchain, these NFTs combine the retro vibes of old school music collections characterized in the main MixTape Headz NFTs collection with various themes from the beautiful Ukrainian culture. #StandWithUkraine
